   },
   {
    "with": "M.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Final draft attached—v2. All metadata scrubbed. Please check the section on the procurement links—it's sensitive. Надеюсь, всё в порядке.",
    "time": "2026-05-07T23:53:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Diaspora contact",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thanks for the invite, but I'm buried in a deadline and can't make it tonight. Have a good one!",
    "time": "2026-05-09T19:09:42"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother (Dilnoza)",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Bolam, bugun Samarkandda juda issiq, shamol ham yo'q. Otang ko'chada o'tiribdi, lekin ko'zi biroz og'riyapti. O'zingni ehtiyot qil, ishlar bilan charchama.",
    "time": "2026-05-18T11:30:13"
   },
   {
    "with": "Editor M.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Received the files—checked the checksums. The procurement link is there, but we need to verify the second batch. Let's sync on SimpleX.",
    "time": "2026-05-21T00:26:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother (Dilnoza)",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Rahmat, oyijon. Siz bilan gaplashganim yaxshi bo'ldi. Otangni ko'rib xursand bo'ldim. O'zingizni ehtiyot qiling.",
    "time": "2026-05-24T15:17:25"
   },
   {
    "with": "Diaspora Contact",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Thanks for the invite, but I'm buried in a deadline. Have a great dinner with everyone!",
    "time": "2026-05-24T19:46:18"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother — Dilnoza",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Assalomu alaykum, Oyijon. Good morning. How is Father's blood pressure today? I hope the weather in Samarkand is nice. I'll call you on Sunday as usual. Love you.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T11:28:21"
   },
   {
    "with": "Editor — M.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Found a lead on the agricultural subsidies—possible overlap with the 2024 procurement scandal. Need to verify the paper trail before we commit. Let me know if you have capacity for a deep dive.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T13:53:55"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother — Dilnoza",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Salom, qizim. Everything is fine here. Your brother Sardor's wife is asking about you. The weather is getting cold. Don't work too late, okay? Pray for us.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T11:07:23"
   },
   {
    "with": "'the Accountant'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Checking in. Are we still on the protocol? Confirm receipt of the last sync.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T13:59:41"
   },
   {
    "with": "Editor — M.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Regarding Thursday—I'll have the draft in the Nextcloud folder by 22:00. Need to double-check the metadata on the latest leak first.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T17:38:45"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother — Dilnoza",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Oyijon, just checking in. How is the garden? Did Father take his medicine? Thinking of you both.",
    "time": "2026-05-29T12:06:10"
   },
   {
    "with": "'the Accountant'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "It has been too long. Please, just a signal. Are you safe?",
    "time": "2026-05-30T15:21:15"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother — Dilnoza",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Qizim, that call was very emotional. Please, just be careful. We are praying for you.",
    "time": "2026-05-31T10:51:53"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother — Dilnoza",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Oyijon, I had to run to a meeting. I'll call you properly on Sunday. Please tell Father I love him. Everything is fine here in Tbilisi.",
    "time": "2026-05-31T18:36:25"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother (Dilnoza)",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Bolam, how is the weather in Tbilisi? Your father's blood pressure is a bit high today. Don't forget to eat. Everything is fine here, just the usual dust.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T11:34:14"
   },
